Published figure: 
<bibRefCitation id="EF924B342867FFF0F6E9FE83FD59B122" author="DeVries" box="[398,762,260,285]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" refString="DeVries, P. J. &amp; Poinar, G. O. (1997) Ancient butterfly-ant symbiosis: direct evidence from Dominican amber. Proceedings of the Royal Society of London B, 264, 1137 - 1140." type="journal article" year="1997">
DeVries &amp; Poinar (1997: 
<figureCitation id="13382A402867FFF0F5CAFE83FD4DB122" box="[685,750,260,285]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="4.[151,250,1051,1073]" captionTargetBox="[167,1414,420,1017]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[157,1429,411,1026]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 1. Localities of fossil butterflies plotted ion a modern map. See Table 1 for further, complementary information." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/583184/files/figure.png" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
